column5: Had another good day out.Although no Whities or lakers. A couple of Herring and a lot of good size perch. Sorry for the quality of this picture,but left my camera in the sleigh for about 8 hours in the cold. Couldn't get the lens to clear up even after hour with the heat on in the hut.Checked it now and it's working ok. Ended up with about 50 total for the day.Even the MNR officer stopped by to visit
Sure, sure...... I think someones been smokin something  in that hut!!! JK  Good Fishing
Nice catch  Any chance I know where you were?
Yes,but even further out. Never seen the average size in a day to be that big.
Good job Davey!!!  Sounds like the perch was biting pretty good   Enjoy the fish fry
What's with all the steam? Don't tell me you installed a solar shower in that thing
Looks like you cleaned up pretty well out there. Nice Job.
Nice haul !!!! Looks like you were hot-boxing your hut !!!! Lol... What time is dinner???
